---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Tools" description="Browser-local worksheets for reviewing pay-plan mechanics and illustrating a narrow wages-only scenario.">
  <main id="main-content">
    <header class="tools-hero shell"><p class="eyebrow">Educational instruments · inputs stay local</p><h1>Make the assumptions visible.</h1><p class="lede">These tools organize inputs and surface review questions. They do not determine compliance, liability, or value.</p></header>
    <section class="shell section tool-list">
      <a href="/tools/pay-plan-check/"><span>01</span><div><p>Pay-plan worksheet</p><h2>Check a pay plan.</h2><small>Compare recorded time, paid time, incentive mechanics, rest-period presentation, and written terms.</small></div><b>→</b></a>
      <a href="/tools/exposure-snapshot/"><span>02</span><div><p>Wages-only model</p><h2>Build an exposure snapshot.</h2><small>Multiply a narrow set of assumptions and keep every excluded category beside the result.</small></div><b>→</b></a>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .tools-hero { padding-block: var(--space-9); }
  .tools-hero h1 { max-width: 65rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .tool-list { border-top: 3px solid var(--color-ink); }
  .tool-list a { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 3rem 1fr 2rem; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; min-height: 17rem; border-bottom: var(--rule); padding-block: 2.5rem; color: var(--color-text); text-decoration: none; }
  .tool-list a:hover { background: var(--color-paper-blue); }
  .tool-list > a > span, .tool-list p { color: var(--color-cobalt-dark); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .tool-list h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .tool-list small { display: block; max-width: 46rem; color: var(--color-muted); font-size: var(--text-body); }
  .tool-list b { color: var(--color-cobalt); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  @media (max-width: 38rem) { .tool-list a { grid-template-columns: 2rem 1fr 1rem; gap: 0.8rem; min-height: 13rem; } }
</style>
